name: Bamboo Fleece Blanket
description: Smallish bamboo fleece blankets are the ultimate in softness and style. They feature an outer layer of 100% cotton designer fabric and an inner layer of super soft organic bamboo fleece (to read more about the amazing properties of bamboo please return to the Smallish website). The blanket is a generous size (30x34" or 76x86cm) which makes it perfect for on the go as well as on the floor at home, in a bassinet or as a throw in babies cot. Each blanket comes with it's own removable coordinating strap to keep the blanket wrapped or folded when its tucked away in a nappy bag. Options 3, 6, 7, 8 & 10 are available for immediate shipping, all other blankets will ship within 4 weeks.

name: Burp Cloth Set/Change Mat
description: Smallish burp cloths come in a huge range of gorgeous colours, and are sold in packs of two coordinating prints. They are made with a double layer of super absorbent bamboo fleece, which not only absorbs whatever baby throws at it, but will also be lovely and soft on their little face to read more about the amazing properties of bamboo please return to the Smallish website). Of course the benefit for mum lies with the gorgeous designer fabrics on the other side! All burp cloth sets are available for immediate shipping.

name: Regular Smallish Quilt
description: Smallish crib/cot size reversible quilt is a gorgeous addition to any nursery. Our standard design features one fabric on the front, one on the back and one for the binding. All Smallish quilts are filled with bamboo wadding (to read more about why to choose bamboo go to the Smallish website). Additionally the fabrics available for this quilt are hand printed and very unique. Quilts are 40x47" or 100x120cm making them a great, slightly oversized, fit for a cot and once your baby moves into a 'big' bed they can keep using their Smallish quilt as a throw. They also make excellent cubby house roofs! This quilt is custom made with your choice of fabrics from the two ranges shown in the images. Please select one fabric for the front, one for the back and one for the binding and enter these choices as you check out. Fabric selections will be confirmed once payment has been received. Your quilt will ship in 6-8 weeks. We can also make all your bedding sheets and accessories, so please have a look around at our range of options.
